query:
/*+  */ select count(account.display_name)
from badge AS b2
inner join so_user AS so_user
on b2.site_id = so_user.site_id AND b2.user_id = so_user.id AND b2.name = 'API Beta'
inner join account AS account
on account.id = so_user.account_id AND account.website_url <> ''
inner join badge AS b1
on b2.date > b1.date + '4 months'::interval AND b1.site_id = so_user.site_id AND b1.user_id = so_user.id AND b1.name = 'Caucus';
